        "\n",
        "### Activity 3: Debug a false proof\n",
        "\n",
        "Ask:\n",
        "\n",
        "> A student claims that if $A$ and $B$ are symmetric, then $AB$ is symmetric. Find the mistake and give a counterexample.\n",
